name: PROPERTIES 04 - Theater in Little Nostalgia
description:
The following NFT corresponds to the collection of properties located in Kitty City in the Little Nostalgia neighborhood. 
This 105 year old property is one of the oldest in our city, with space to hold up to 40 people or 120 cats as audience. 
Its acoustics are unbeatable and its shows stand out mainly for representing the most popular Kitty King books. 
With the purchase of your ticket they give you a small snack for the function. 
Enjoy the show! 
Land measurements: 90m x 80m
